 Destructor stood up."The chamber is here? Excelent. That is one of the most 
powerful defensive ships in history. But it is not yet complete. Magnus I 
will tell Kit Kat to mover her troops to the new base. We will have to bring 
dark sentinel to the chamber plus all the autoguns and defensive computers. I 
will tell Kit Kat..you get started." 
  The two destrons sphink and his friend started to disassemble dark 
sentinel.  Whil Magnus and gabriel went out side and took down the autoguns. 
All the while destructor sent a repeated mess to Kit Kat.."We are moveing to 
the new base. I know this is sudden but you will know why soon. The destrons 
flew off towards the chamber with dark sentinel.
